{"wrapper":"div#el-blog-template","sections":{"blog-title":{"type":"blog-title","settings":{"color":"","blog-title":"12 CLASSIC FASHION PIECES EVERY WARDROBE NEEDS","title_color":"","blog-title-font-size":48,"mobile-font-size":22,"alignment":"center"}},"1663872094552ff4cb":{"type":"custom-content-01","blocks":{"60fc0c85-ddcf-4402-bba2-ac04477bc5ac":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_1.jpg","width":"100%","alignment":"center","image_alignment":"center"}},"1663872094b49339eb-0":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":20,"title_font_weight":400,"text":"<p>Trends come and go with the seasons, but some styles that transcend the years. As we all look to shop more sustainably, curating a wardrobe of basic, fundamental pieces that can be styled with one another is a step in the eco-friendly direction. Here are 12 staples that no rotation should be without. <\/p>","content_color":"#000000","text_font_size":20,"margin_top":0,"border_top":0,"border_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":50,"width":"50%","alignment":"center","align_text":"left"}}},"block_order":["60fc0c85-ddcf-4402-bba2-ac04477bc5ac","1663872094b49339eb-0"],"settings":{"title":""}},"1663868435f0c44a9a":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"#000000","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>1. The button-up shirt <br\/><\/strong><\/em><br\/>A plain white and crisp button-up shirt can be styled with jeans - oversized and French-tucked - or can form part of your boardroom attire. Have one pressed and hanging in your wardrobe ready to go. <\/p>","text-color":"#000000","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_2.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"16638720430f34827e":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>2. The perfect jeans<\/strong><\/em>  <br\/><br\/>Denim is a wardrobe staple; easy to wear and looks great with almost anything. Vintage and straight-leg styles are preferred nowadays, and pair with everything from a plain T-shirt to a smart shirt. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_3.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"166387328793cd4683":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>3. The little black dress <br\/><\/strong><\/em><br\/>No wardrobe is complete without a Little Black Dress. Choose one that is flattering and timeless, that can be worn for a multitude of occasions with different styling here and there. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_4.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"166387221970bc3eb0":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>4. The white tee<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>A crisp white T-shirt is an essential part of your everyday wardrobe. It goes with practically anything; from a chunky knit cardigan to a smart blazer. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_5.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"f82e9674-462e-405d-abe8-0768e14e9810":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>5. The camel trench <\/strong><\/em><\/p><p>Never skimp on your outerwear, especially when the colder seasons come around. A trench coat in a camel or beige shade can work for any occasion and is easy to throw on over whatever you’re wearing. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_6.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"0e350e92-8dc7-447c-ae4a-6ac4d056be03":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>6. The blazer<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>Smarten up in an instant. Whether there’s an important meeting in your diary or you need to liven up the classic ‘jeans and a nice top’ look, a blazer in a neutral shade - such as a jet black or navy blue - will add instant chic. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_7.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"77023ddc-5418-49ba-a866-7237d2a3c23d":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>7. The cosy jumper<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>The perfect knit is a must-have. Make the right choice and it will transfer from day to night seamlessly. Go for a classic button-down cardigan or a soft cashmere jumper; both pair easily with our other choices here. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_8.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"c1c906e7-71d9-4250-8f74-a921f1e6505e":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>8. The work trousers <\/strong><\/em><br\/><br\/>Jeans and luxe tracksuits have their place, but when the occasion calls for something smarter, reach for a pair of trousers. Cropped trousers that end just above the ankle can be paired with sandals or trainers. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_10.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"280d8c16-4bd1-4f60-bb83-305afdd061c5":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>9. The go-anywhere tote<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>Invest in the right bag and you will have it for years to come. A classic tote can be used for your daily essentials to the odd purchase. Avoid bright colours and stick to neutrals so you can pick up and go regardless of your day.<\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_11.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"25994b09-56cb-4141-a7db-d1d9bd59dd47":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>10. The classic hoops<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>Rather than debate your jewellery choices every morning, reach for stylish and timeless pieces. Small hoops that sit delicately in your lobes - in silver or gold - are the perfect choice.  <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_12.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"519bdc52-efc6-4fd9-9698-ff14fabd505b":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>11. The pure white trainers<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>When you’re on the go, you need to be comfortable. Don’t compromise your style and opt for clean white trainers that you can slip into to run all your errands.  <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_13.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"3af231cb-21bd-427b-a9c2-9bfc060d6d6b":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>12. The loafers<\/strong><\/em>  <br\/><br\/>For functional work shoes that don’t send you back to primary school, look no further than the loafer. Tan or black work best for easy outfit transition. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/12_classic_fashion_pieces_every_wardrobe_needs_14.jpg","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b":{"type":"custom-content-01","blocks":{"template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-0":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Talk about your brand","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":35,"title_font_weight":400,"text":"","content_color":"#000000","text_font_size":25,"margin_top":30,"border_top":1,"border_color":"","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":30,"width":"50%","alignment":"center","align_text":"left"}},"template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-1":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"width":"50%","alignment":"center","image_alignment":"center"}},"a088c57c-ac2c-486a-adae-1cd9241f0b6d":{"type":"cta","settings":{"padding-top":24,"title":"Shop Essentials","url":"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/cashmere-essentials","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":32,"cta_bg":"","cta_border_color":"","cta_border":1,"align_text":"center"}}},"block_order":["template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-0","template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e